rows.label: qst201407_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, Hikari and Zakuro... Are ye
really havin' a Girl Power showdown?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0002
rows.name: Well, if it isn't Saika.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0003
rows.name:
Chat with us and judge which
of us has more Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0004
rows.name: Sounds interestin'. Alright.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0005
rows.name: So, what were ye talkin' about?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0006
rows.name: So far, favorite foods and crushes.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0007
rows.name: Ho, crushes, eh...?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0008
rows.name:
Do ye two have anyone
ye're interested in?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0009
rows.name:
Hmm, I'm interested in love, but
there's no one like that right now.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0010
rows.name: Me neither, not really...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0011
rows.name:
What's with that answer, Hikari?
Ye're not bein' very clear.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0012
rows.name:
Are ye sure there isn't
someone? For example...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0013
rows.name: Ah! No, there isn't!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0014
rows.name: What about you, Saika?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0015
rows.name: Yeah!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0016
rows.name: How are things with Zeke? Any progress?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0017
rows.name:
N-No! The Prince and
I aren't like that!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0018
rows.name:
The Prince is too dense
to notice anything...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0019
rows.name:
The way you say that means you
are interested, aren't you?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0020
rows.name: What do you really think? Tell us!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0021
rows.name: N-No way, no way!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0022
rows.name: I'm absolutely not tellin'!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0023
rows.name: She ran away...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0024
rows.name: Saika's surprisingly shy...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0025
rows.name:
The judge is gone again, so
this one is also a draw.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0026
rows.name: I suppose it can't be helped...
